<strong>Before clicking Search below:</strong>
<p style="padding-left: 1rem; text-indent: -0.8rem">1. Open <a href="https://matrix.itasoftware.com" target="_blank">Matrix</a>.</p>
<p style="padding-left: 1rem; text-indent: -0.8rem">2. Ensure that <strong>Routing Codes</strong> and <strong>Extension Codes</strong> fields are shown, under the <strong>Origin</strong> and <strong>Destination</strong> fields.</p>
<p style="padding-left: 1rem; text-indent: -0.8rem">3. If not, click <strong>Show Advanced Controls</strong>.</p>
